d:["$","article",null,{"className":"bg-white","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-6","children":["$","nav",null,{"className":"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600","children":[["$","$L5",null,{"href":"/","className":"hover:text-blue-600","children":"Home"}],[["$","div","/car-seats",{"className":"flex items-center space-x-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-gray-400","children":"/"}],["$","$L5",null,{"href":"/car-seats","className":"hover:text-blue-600","children":"Car Seats"}]]}],["$","div","/car-seats/best-car-seats-for-small-cars",{"className":"flex items-center space-x-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-gray-400","children":"/"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-gray-900 font-medium","children":"Best Car Seats for Small Cars and Narrow Back Seats"}]]}]]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 border-b border-gray-200","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Best Car Seats for Small Cars and Narrow Back Seats"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-lg text-gray-600","children":"Find car seats that fit in compact vehicles. Discover the narrowest, most space-efficient car seats ideal for compact cars, sedans, and vehicles with tight back seat space."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700","children":[["$","h2","0",{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4","children":"Introduction"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"Small cars, compact sedans, and hatchbacks present unique challenges for car seat installation. Narrow back seats, limited recline angles, and tight spacing mean that not all car seats fit equally well. A full-size convertible that requires 30 inches of front-to-back space may be impossible to install in a compact vehicle. This guide identifies the best car seats optimized for small cars and explains how to measure compatibility before purchase."}],["$","h2","2",{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4","children":"Why Small Cars Are Challenging"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"Most car seats are designed for full-size SUVs and sedans with spacious back seats. When installing a car seat in a compact vehicle, you encounter three constraints:"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"1. **Seat width** — Narrow back seats may not accommodate wider seats\n2. **Installation space** — Reclined rear-facing installation requires clearance from the front seat\n3. **Seat height** — Some seats have tall profiles that hit low car ceilings"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"A car seat rated for a full-size sedan may physically install in a compact car, but the front seat will be pushed so far forward that front-row passengers lose all legroom."}],["$","h2","6",{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4","children":"Car Seat Width: The Critical Measurement"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"The most important specification for small cars is seat width. Narrow car seats (under 17.5 inches) fit three across small vehicle back seats. Wider seats (18+ inches) typically fit only two across."}],["$","h2","8",{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4","children":"#Widest vs Narrowest Car Seats"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"**Narrowest (fits in tight spaces):**\n- Maxi-Cosi Mico Luxe: 16.75 inches\n- Clek Fllo: 17.5 inches\n- Graco SlimFit3 LX: 17.5 inches\n- Chicco KeyFit 35: 17.5 inches\n- UPPAbaby Mesa Max: 17.25 inches"}],"$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25","$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d","$L2e","$L2f","$L30","$L31","$L32","$L33","$L34","$L35","$L36","$L37","$L38","$L39","$L3a","$L3b","$L3c","$L3d","$L3e","$L3f","$L40","$L41","$L42","$L43","$L44","$L45","$L46","$L47","$L48","$L49","$L4a","$L4b","$L4c","$L4d","$L4e","$L4f","$L50","$L51","$L52","$L53","$L54","$L55","$L56","$L57","$L58","$L59","$L5a","$L5b","$L5c"]}]}],"$L5d","$L5e"]}]
